item.title: About me
item.author: rokas@sutkusaudio.com (Rokas Sutkus)
item.description: The creative side I’m absolutely enamored with the world of sound â€“ like the moments when a wind chime’s melody carries you away or when you feel the power of bass deeply in your bones. There’s something about the mix of highs and lows, not to mention those futuristic synthesizer sounds straight out of a sci-fi flick. It’s like each sound has its own story to tell, and I’m all ears for it.
